                <p>Organic reach is not only more affordable but also more effective in building trust. Customers are more likely to engage with businesses recommended by peers rather than random ads.</p>
                <p>By working together with other business owners, you ensure steady traffic to your business while supporting others in return—a win-win strategy for sustainable growth.</p>
            </div>

            <!-- Section 4 -->
            <div class="mb-5">
                <h3><i class="bi bi-lightbulb text-primary"></i> Learn and Stay Inspired</h3>
